E4Plus1.uk.description: El Cantito: Gordon helps a Puerto Rican restaurant in Yonkers, New York, which struggled when Covid hit. Appliances break, uncooked chicken is served... Can Gordon turn it around? (S8 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Big Baby Ball: When Coach Mellor singles out Adam during dodgeball, Beverly intervenes and gets him fired. But then Murray and Adam see Mellor in a new light. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Goldberg Thanksgiving: Beverly challenges Erica to participate in Jazzercise after Erica says her mum's obsession is sad. Marvin visits the family at Thanksgiving. (S2 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Deep Space Homer: NASA recruit Homer and Barney to make the organisation more appealing to the common man. When Barney has too much to drink, Homer is chosen to go into space. (S5 Ep15/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer the Heretic: Homer has a vision from God and decides to start his own religion, which doesn't go down too well with the neighbours. (S4 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mr Plow: Homer impulsively buys a snow plough and sets up in business as Mr Plow. But when Barney declares himself the Plow King, their rivalry spirals out of control. (S4 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge vs the Monorail: When Springfield decides to install a monorail system, Homer is employed as the conductor. There's just one problem: he has no idea what he's doing. (S4 Ep12/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pokey Mom: Marge notices a prison inmate's artistic talent and helps him to get a job painting a mural at the school. But he clashes with Skinner. Michael Keaton guest stars. (S12 Ep10/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Worst Episode Ever: Bart and Milhouse end up running Comic Book Guy's shop after he has a heart attack. And, while he recovers, Comic Book Guy falls in love... (S12 Ep11/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Sonic the Hedgehog
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2020) Madcap adventure-comedy video game adaptation with Jim Carrey and Ben Schwartz. Can nippy ring-chasing hedgehog Sonic escape the clutches of an evil, moustachioed scientist?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Raya and the Last Dragon
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2021) Awkwafina is the last dragon and Kelly Marie Tran is Raya - the young woman on a quest to save her homeland from the agents of chaos in Disney's magical animated family epic.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Last Exit to Springfield: Homer takes on Mr Burns in a labour struggle that rapidly spirals out of control after Homer leads the workers on strike. (S4 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Hungry Hungry Homer: Homer goes on hunger strike when he discovers that the Springfield Isotopes baseball team are planning to move to Albuquerque. (S12 Ep15/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Please Homer Don't Hammer 'Em: Marge discovers that she has a gift for carpentry, but has to use Homer as a cover in order to overcome prejudices against women builders. (S18 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: G.I. (Annoyed Grunt): Homer accidentally signs up for basic training in the army. And Marge and Grampa get roped in when they try to get him released. (S18 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ice Cream of Margie (With the Light Blue Hair): Marge, feeling overshadowed by Homer's new career selling ice cream, starts creating ice lolly stick sculptures. (S18 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E My Sports: When Bart starts earning money from video game competitions, Homer becomes his coach, and their team make it to the finals in South Korea. (S30 Ep17/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Bart's Birthday: Bart has to organise his own birthday party when Homer forgets to post the invitations. Mr Burns fakes his own death. (S36 Ep1/18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - The Yellow Lotus: The Simpsons stumble across a mystery and an old enemy while they're on holiday at a peculiar island resort. Dr Hibbert drugs an otter. (S36 Ep2/18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox for Stand...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Up To Cancer: Celebrities join the Gogglebox regulars to react to our top telly in this special episode for Stand Up To Cancer. (S24 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Free Guy
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2021) Comedy action starring Ryan Reynolds. Guy lives in Free City. Free City isn't real. Nor is Guy. It's all a big online game. Can he take down the corrupt game publisher?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pansexual Sarah can't wait to road test her new body on her first date as a woman. Plumber Jamie's love life has gone down the u-bend, so he's all cisterns go to find a partner. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pansexual sex therapist Mariia's after a not-so-average Mr or Mrs who's not too tired for sex. Old romantic at heart Alannah seeks a forever fella who can speak her love language. (S11 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox for Stand...

E4Plus1.uk.description: Sonny is a party fanatic. How will his bride Jazmin greet his plans for a zoo-themed Ibizan beach party wedding with everyone covered in animal-print body paint?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Lego Masters Australia
E4Plus1.uk.description: City in the Sky: Previous winners and finalists return for a Grand Masters special series. First up, they must create a world suspended high in the sky. (S5 Ep1) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Da Mimmo: Gordon tries to transform New Jersey Italian restaurant Da Mimmo, which is run by a mother and her three sons - two of whom see the business as a failure... (S8 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Juicy Box: Gordon helps a Haitian juice bar and restaurant in Brooklyn. Jacques opened the Juicy Box to provide healthier options for the neighbourhood, but it's fallen into chaos. (S8 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Playing with Fire
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Fun-filled family comedy starring John Cena. A macho fireman has to babysit three impish kids after saving them from a blaze in the remote California woodlands.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Secret Headquarters
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2022) Family comedy with Michael Pea. A young lad discovers that his slacker dad is a superhero. And before he's got used to the idea, he must foil a villain's plot to bring his dad down.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great New Year Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: As the oven timers strike midnight, teams of legendary bakers from seasons gone by bring in 2026 the only way they know how... with fabulous festive baking and plenty of merry making. [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: You Only Move Twice: Homer is offered a new job by mysterious businessman Hank Scorpio. But will Marge, Bart and Lisa be happy in their idyllic new home town? (S8 Ep2/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Hurricane Neddy: The Flanders' home is blown down by a hurricane and the Leftorium is looted. Homer leads the rebuilding project, but will Ned be happy with his new house? (S8 Ep8/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Springfield Files: Homer thinks he's seen an alien in the woods. This could be a case for Mulder and Scully (guest stars David Duchovny and Gillian Anderson). (S8 Ep10/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Aladdin
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Guy Ritchie's vigorously lamp-rubbing musical remake of the Disney classic, starring Will Smith as the genie. Can urchin Aladdin raise himself up and capture the princess's heart?

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer's Phobia: Homer's prejudices surface when Bart befriends a gay shop owner (guest star John Waters). So he decides to take Bart hunting - but it doesn't go to plan. (S8 Ep15/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer vs the Eighteenth Amendment: When alcohol is banned in Springfield, Moe's Tavern becomes a speakeasy and Homer re-invents himself as the Beer Baron. (S8 Ep18/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Canine Mutiny: Bart buys Laddie, an amazing new dog, with a credit card that's accidentally been sent to Santa's Little Helper. (S8 Ep20/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Old Man and the Lisa: Mr Burns loses all his money and employs Lisa to help him earn back his fortune. But they don't see eye to eye over ethical issues. (S8 Ep21/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer and Apu: When Apu loses the Kwik-E-Mart, he moves in with the Simpsons. And then Homer joins him on a pilgrimage to the first ever Kwik-E-Mart, in the Himalayas. (S5 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates: Valentine's Special
E4Plus1.uk.description: Chi-Chi and her son Kurtis visit the restaurant together: can she resist interfering in his date with Jaleesa? And Danny discovers that his date's best friend is First Dates waiter Laura. [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Georgia is looking for a football-playing Cara Delevingne. Josh and Natasha bond over having fabulous hair, but commit some hilarious dining faux pas. (S12 Ep1) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The top TV includes: Strictly Come Dancing, Celebrity SAS: Who Dares Wins, A Very Royal Scandal, The Yorkshire Vet, This Morning (gurning) and My Mum, Your Dad. (S24 Ep3) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.description: The sky's the limit for adrenaline junkie Jai who plans to have a wedding in the sky, even though his bride-to-be Leanne is terrified of heights.

E4Plus1.uk.description: Things are frosty between Misbah and Donny. Leela faces her first Christmas without Peri and extends an olive branch to Ste. And Pearl has something she wants to get off her chest.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.description: The One with the Party Boy Groom: Reluctant Lee devises Las Vegas-style nuptials, but it's not the family church in Norfolk that his bride Anna had in mind.

E4Plus1.uk.description: The One with the Groom Hunt: Groom Lee and his brother take off on a tour of Europe, telling bride Becky that if she wants to marry Lee, she has to find him first.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Kindred: In New Orleans, Gordon helps Kindred, a vegan restaurant grappling with delusion, disorganisation, a hoarder owner and a cook from hell. (S9 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Paw Patrol: The Movie
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2021) Family animation. The plucky pups head to the city to foil dastardly Mayor Humdinger's latest plot. But can Chase overcome his fear of the big smoke and be the hero everyone needs?

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Trilogy of Error: Homer gets his thumb sliced off while trying to steal a brownie. Lisa misses the school bus. Bart discovers Fat Tony's stash of smuggled fireworks. (S12 Ep18/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I'm Goin' to Praiseland: Ned opens a Christian amusement park. At first, the tame religious attractions are unpopular. But then visitors start having visions... (S12 Ep19/21)

E4Plus1.uk.description: Three Dreams Denied: Bart becomes a voiceover actor. Comic Book Guy is humiliated at Comic-Con. And Lisa is set up for a fall. (S32 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Road to Cincinnati: Odd couple Skinner and Chalmers embark on an 800-mile road trip to Cincinnati for an administrators convention. (S32 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.description: (2018) Emily Blunt heads a stellar cast as everyone's favourite flying nanny. Can she help the grown-up Banks kids keep their home? With Meryl Streep, Lin-Manuel Miranda and Dick Van Dyke.

E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Desperately Seeking Lisa: Lisa visits Capital City with Patty and Selma, where she's swept up in the city's art scene. But the big city's got an underbelly. (S36 Ep3/18)

E4Plus1.uk.description: (2022) Comedy adventure with Sandra Bullock and Channing Tatum. When a romance novelist is kidnapped wearing a pink jumpsuit, her hapless cover model heads to the jungle to rescue her.

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Whitby to Robin Hood's Bay: Michael Portillo travels from Whitby, where he explores the port's shipbuilding and seafaring heritage, to Robin Hood's Bay, a former smuggling haven. S2 Ep7

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The Thin Blue Line
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Ism Ism Ism: Rowan Atkinson teams up again with Blackadder writer Ben Elton for the police station sitcom. Fowler faces an asylum seeker and Grim faces up to a dead turkey's bottom. S2 Ep2

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The Thin Blue Line
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Fly on the Wall: Ben Elton and Rowan Atkinson join forces again in the hilarious police sitcom. A BBC crew comes to Gasforth to make a documentary about policing in the raw. S2 Ep3

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Porridge
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Just Desserts: Ronnie Barker in one of his best roles as habitual criminal Fletcher. The inmates are horrified to discover that there's a thief in their midst. Surely not... S2 Ep1

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Porridge
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Heartbreak Hotel: When Godber gets some bad news from his girlfriend, Fletcher is on hand to provide advice. Could Ingrid be a possible solution? Classic prison comedy. S2 Ep2

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Disturbing the Peace: When Mr McKay leaves Slade prison, everyone is happy - until his replacement arrives. Contains outdated language. S2 Ep3

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Red Dwarf
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Body Swap: A classic episode of the enduring space comedy. Chaos ensues when the ship's circuitry is rewired by a Skutter, ending up with Lister loaning his body to Rimmer. S3 Ep4

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Red Dwarf
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Timeslides: Smegging hilarious space sitcom. The crew discover a mutated developing fluid that allows them to travel to any place or time of which they have a photo. Cue mayhem. S3 Ep5

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Red Dwarf
UAndYesterday.uk.description: The Last Day: The sitcom set on a dysfunctional spaceship. Kryten discovers that his in-built expiry date gives him less than 24 hours to live, so the perfect send-off is called for. S3 Ep6

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Guy Martin's D-Day Landing

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Austin 7 Chummy/Triumph TR4A: Derek picks up a lovingly restored 1925 Calthorpe motorbike that he thinks is more of a work of art than anything ever produced by Picasso. S7 Ep1

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Swift/Toyota Corona/Bedford Van: Derek goes to pick up a veteran 1904 Swift, there's an emotional farewell to a 1980s Bedford HA van, and a Toyota Corona finds a new home. S9 Ep4

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: MGYB / Yamaha / Quattro: Derek gives the once-over to a Royale Formula Ford race car, and Paul is on a marathon trip to pick up a 1953 MGYB, a Moggy Van, and an '80s Yamaha 250RD motorbike. S9 Ep5

UAndYesterday.uk.description: Whirlwind: The ultimate guide to World War II, narrated by Laurence Olivier. Bomber Command are unable to hit their targets precisely and attack German cities under cover of darkness. S1 Ep12

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Tough Old Gut: The hugely respected chronology of WWII. Churchill described Italy as the 'soft underbelly of the crocodile', thinking the Allies could cut through it to reach Germany. S1 Ep13

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterday.uk.description: It's a Lovely Day Tomorrow: Laurence Olivier narrates the acclaimed documentary series on WWII. Hear how Japanese advances across Asia forced the Allies into ignominious retreat. S1 Ep14

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Inside the Reich: Laurence Olivier narrates this 26-part series, a milestone in TV history. Germany's progress loses momentum as the tide of the war turns in favour of the Allies. S1 Ep16

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Morning: England became a supply dump as the British and Americans assembled the largest invasion fleet in history for Operation Overlord on 6 June 1944. Laurence Olivier tells all. S1 Ep17

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Occupation: Hear how the Netherlands lived under Nazi rule for four years and how its people decided where their loyalties lay. Narrated by the late, great Laurence Olivier. S1 Ep18

UAndYesterday.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Pincers: Laurence Olivier provides the narration to this World War II retrospective. Hear how 1944 saw the steady disintegration of the German war machine, as the Allies advanced. S1 Ep19

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Blue Planet

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Blue Planet
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Tidal Seas: A history of the deep seas, narrated by Sir David Attenborough. How do the tides affect marine life like stingrays, snails and dolphins? Find out here. S1 Ep7

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Blue Planet
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Coasts: David Attenborough explains in his own inimitable way how animals from in and around the sea manage to make use of the constantly changing areas where land meets water. S1 Ep8

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterday.uk.description: One Ocean: Marine life around the world, from dolphins and tusk fish in a tropical coral reef to walruses struggling to cope with the impact of climate change on the polar north. S2 Ep1

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterday.uk.description: The Deep: Creatures that live in volcanic hot spots on the ocean bed, areas that reach temperatures hot enough to melt lead and which may hold the secrets behind all life on Earth. S2 Ep2

UAndYesterday.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterday.uk.description: Ford Escort Mexico: Derek has sold everything from trucks to bicycles - but he can't remember the last time he auctioned off a two-seater plane. S7 Ep3

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Triumph Herald/Renault Caravelle: Derek swaps the chaos of the office for rain-soaked Ripon to pick up a 1965 Ford Anglia with just 33,000 miles on the clock, while Dave's loving the clean lines of a

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash: Restoring Classics
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Ford Capri: Derek thinks a 29,000-mile Ford Capri should be kept original. Plus, a Hercules women's racing bike from the '50s. S1 Ep4

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Frozen Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Last Frontier: The penultimate part of David Attenborough's acclaimed nature series. This episode looks at us humans, one of the polar regions' most ingenious inhabitants. S1 Ep6

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shopping from Home.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Bomb: The critically acclaimed documentary series all about World War II. Hear about the Allied scientists' controversial efforts to develop a new, immensely powerful weapon. S1 Ep24

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Morning: England became a supply dump as the British and Americans assembled the largest invasion fleet in history for Operation Overlord on 6 June 1944. Laurence Olivier tells all. S1 Ep17

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Occupation: Hear how the Netherlands lived under Nazi rule for four years and how its people decided where their loyalties lay. Narrated by the late, great Laurence Olivier. S1 Ep18

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: The World at War
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Pincers: Laurence Olivier provides the narration to this World War II retrospective. Hear how 1944 saw the steady disintegration of the German war machine, as the Allies advanced. S1 Ep19

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Coral Seas: Stunning film sequences and unusual life-forms abound in Sir David Attenborough's natural history of the oceans, which covers the fragile ecosystems of the coral reefs. S1 Ep6

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Tidal Seas: A history of the deep seas, narrated by Sir David Attenborough. How do the tides affect marine life like stingrays, snails and dolphins? Find out here. S1 Ep7

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Coasts: David Attenborough explains in his own inimitable way how animals from in and around the sea manage to make use of the constantly changing areas where land meets water. S1 Ep8

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: One Ocean: Marine life around the world, from dolphins and tusk fish in a tropical coral reef to walruses struggling to cope with the impact of climate change on the polar north. S2 Ep1

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Blue Planet II
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Deep: Creatures that live in volcanic hot spots on the ocean bed, areas that reach temperatures hot enough to melt lead and which may hold the secrets behind all life on Earth. S2 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Volvo P1800/Morris Milk Float: Dave gets wind of a possible free lunch at the officers' mess when he heads off to collect a stylish Swedish Volvo P1800S from an RAF base in the Midlands. S7 Ep2
